==Galician==
===Etymology===
From Old Galician and {{inh|gl|roa-opt|jur}}, from {{inh|gl|la|jūre}}, {{m|la|iūre}}, ablative of {{m|la|iūs}}, with inflection later altered in Galician and Portuguese, as if a derivative of the verb {{m|gl|xurar}}; compare {{cog|pt|juro}}.
===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|gl|[ˈʃu.ɾʊ]}}
